@@TJvID3v1.Year
Summary
  Specifies the year when this song has originally been released.
Description
  Use Year to specify the year when this song has originally been released. Maximal length of the
  \string is 4.
  
  Before reading or setting Year, you must set Active to true.
See Also
  TJvID3v1.Album, TJvID3v1.AlbumTrack, TJvID3v1.Artist, TJvID3v1.Comment, TJvID3v1.Genre,
  TJvID3v1.SongName

