@@TJvID3v1.Refresh
Summary
  Rereads the ID3v1 tag.
Description
  Call Refresh to reread the tag from the file specified by FileName. Active must have been set to
  true before calling Refresh.
See Also
  TJvID3v1.Active, TJvID3v1.HasTag, TJvID3v1.Open

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvID3v1.SongName
Summary
  Specifies the title of the MP3.
Description
  Use SongName to specify the title of the MP3. Maximal length of the \string is 30.
  
  Before reading or setting SongName, you must set Active to true.
See Also
  TJvID3v1.Album, TJvID3v1.AlbumTrack, TJvID3v1.Artist, TJvID3v1.Comment, TJvID3v1.Genre,
  TJvID3v1.Year

