@@HasID3v1Tag
<TITLE HasID3v1Tag function>
Summary
  Indicates whether a file has an ID3v1 tag.
Description
  Call HasID3v1Tag to determine whether the file specified by parameter AFileName has an ID3v1 tag.
  HasID3v1Tag returns true if the file has an ID3v1 tag, otherwise returns false.
Parameters
  AFileName - Specifies the name of the file.
See Also
  ReadID3v1Tag, RemoveID3v1Tag, WriteID3v1Tag

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@ReadID3v1Tag
<TITLE ReadID3v1Tag function>
Summary
  Reads an ID3v1 tag from a file.
Description
  Call ReadID3v1Tag to retrieve an ID3v1 tag from a file specified by parameter AFileName.
  ReadID3v1Tag \returns true when the tag data has been successful read from the file, and returns
  false if the file has <I>no</I> tag or an error occurred.
Parameters
  AFileName - Specifies the name of the file.
  ATag      - Contains the tag data after a successful call.
See Also
  HasID3v1Tag, RemoveID3v1Tag, WriteID3v1Tag

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@WriteID3v1Tag
<TITLE WriteID3v1Tag function>
Summary
  Writes an ID3v1 tag to a file.
Description
  Call WriteID3v1Tag to write an ID3v1 tag to a file specified by parameter AFileName. WriteID3v1Tag
  returns true when the tag data has been successful written to the file, and returns false if an
  error occurred.
Parameters
  AFileName - Specifies the name of the file.
  ATag      - Specifies the new tag data for the file.
See Also
  HasID3v1Tag, ReadID3v1Tag, RemoveID3v1Tag

